      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·清廟之什·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">維清.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>維清緝熙，文王之典。
肇禋。迄用有成，維周之禎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Clear and to be preserved bright,
Are the statutes of king Wăn.
From the first sacrifice (to him),
Till now when they have issued in our complete state,
They have been the happy omen of (the fortunes of) Kâu.</seg>
      </tuv>
